data.description: Reduced, reduced - Sellers have made this beautiful home ready for a new buyer with a BRAND NEW ROOF and NEW AC completed!! This fabulous home is located in delightful Orange City on a dead-in road - very quiet street.    With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and almost 1800+ sq dt.  ., it boasts great vaulted ceilings, and is close to shopping and restaurants. This home has a beautiful stucco brick exterior that never needs painting. As you walk into the home, you will find a nice open foyer opening to the living room and formal dining room with vaulted ceilings or straight into the kitchen / dinette area.  There is a family room off the dinette that has nice windows with plenty of natural light.  This is a split bedroom plan and the master bedroom has a nice walk-in closet.  It has a welcoming front open porch and also a back porch. Part of the back porch was enclosed into a storage area but could be converted back to open porch. The beautiful back yard features mature oak trees and  fencing.  This quiet dead-end street is a peaceful location to start your new life in your new home.
